'''Ayd<U+0131>n Karabulut''' (born 25 January 1988, [[Berlin]]) is a [[Turkey|Turkish]]-[[Germany|German]] [[football (soccer)|footballer]]. He currently plays for [[Turkey|Turkish]] [[S<U+00FC>per Lig|Super Lig]] club [[Sivasspor]].

==Career==
Ayd<U+0131>n had started his career in [[Hertha BSC Berlin|Hertha Berlin]], one of the leading teams in [[Berlin|German capital]] where he was born. After a while, he pulled the attention of [[Turkey national football team|Turkish national team]] scouts as a promising starlet. He had 5 caps for U-19 national team. He joined Be<U+015F>ikta<U+015F> January 2006. His contract came into force on 8 February 2006 which will expire in May 2010. Ayd<U+0131>n had several recent occasions on [[Turkcell Super League]] in first season mostly as a substitute player.

On 16 February 2008, he was on the line-up of team up against [[Ankaraspor]] where Ayd<U+0131>n assisted [[Mert Nobre|Nobre]] by his corner kick. Subsequently, he tried to find the net by his own again with a corner kick, however he was denied by the opponent keeper [[<U+0160>tefan Seneck<U+00FD>|Seneck<U+00FD>]] after his direct curving shoot.<ref>[http://www.milliyet.com.tr/2008/02/16/son/sonspo26.asp?prm=1512345456 Be<U+015F>ikta<U+015F>:3 <U+2013> Ankaraspor:2 (Result)] {{tr icon}}</ref> He scored his first ever goal for Be<U+015F>ikta<U+015F> on 5 January 2008 in [[Fortis Turkey Cup]] group match against [[Diyarbak<U+0131>r B<U+00FC>y<U+00FC>k<U+015F>ehir Belediye D<U+0130>SK<U+0130> Spor|Diyarbak<U+0131>r B<U+015E>B]].<ref>[http://www.milliyet.com.tr/2008/01/06/spor/spo01.html 2008 model Kartal] {{tr icon}}</ref> Ayd<U+0131>n kept playing as a substitute player for his team and scored his very first goal in [[Turkish Super League|Turkish League]] on a crucial encounter against [[Trabzonspor]].<ref>[http://hurarsiv.hurriyet.com.tr/goster/haber.aspx?id=8471957&tarih=2008-03-16 Kartal Tepeden Bak<U+0131>yor] {{tr icon}}</ref>

Ayd<U+0131>n has joined capital city team [[Ankaraspor A.<U+015E>.|Ankaraspor]] in summer 2009, in return of [[Erhan G<U+00FC>ven]], who joined Be<U+015F>ikta<U+015F> as the new defender.<ref>[http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/spor/futbol/11835252.asp Ayd<U+0131>n Karabulut Ankaraspor'da] {{tr icon}}</ref>

On 6 September 2013, Karabulut left [[Elaz<U+0131><U+011F>spor]] and joined fellow [[S<U+00FC>per Lig|Super Lig]] side [[Sivasspor]].<ref>http://www.sivasspor.org.tr/tr/haber/rafik-djebbour-ve-aydin-karabulut-sivasspor-da#.UjbPQMakpw4</ref>

